    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is an immaculate 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen represents the pinnacle of M-division engineering, boasting a factory-spec limited-slip differential and perfectly calibrated MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry. The mechanical condition is superlative; the notorious VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory standards. Zero fluid seepage is present, and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies remains razor-sharp. Finished in Alpine White with a flawless interior, this vehicle retains its original aerodynamic undertrays and heat shielding. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically synchronized, showroom-quality icon with exhaustive service documentation.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
